#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn36.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn36.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 36 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 36 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Sagāthāvagga "
msgstr "1. With Verses "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn36.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Daṭṭhabbasutta "
msgstr "5. Should Be Seen "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn36.5:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, vedanā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three feelings. "

msgctxt "sn36.5:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso? "
msgstr "What three? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.5:1.3"
msgid "Sukhā vedanā, dukkhā vedanā, adukkhamasukhā vedanā. "
msgstr "Pleasant, painful, and neutral feeling. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.5:1.4"
msgid "Sukhā, bhikkhave, vedanā dukkhato daṭṭhabbā, dukkhā vedanā sallato daṭṭhabbā, adukkhamasukhā vedanā aniccato daṭṭhabbā. "
msgstr "Pleasant feeling should be seen as suffering. Painful feeling should be seen as a dart. Neutral feeling should be seen as impermanent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.5:1.5"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno sukhā vedanā dukkhato diṭṭhā hoti, dukkhā vedanā sallato diṭṭhā hoti, adukkhamasukhā vedanā aniccato diṭṭhā hoti—"
msgstr "When a mendicant has seen these three feelings in this way, "

msgctxt "sn36.5:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ‘bhikkhu sammaddaso acchecchi taṇhaṃ, vivattayi saṃyojanaṃ, sammā mānābhisamayā antamakāsi dukkhassā’ti. "
msgstr "they’re called a mendicant who has cut off craving, untied the fetters, and by rightly comprehending conceit has made an end of suffering. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn36.5:2.1"
msgid "Yo sukhaṃ dukkhato adda, "
msgstr "A mendicant who sees pleasure as pain, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn36.5:2.2"
msgid "dukkhamaddakkhi sallato; "
msgstr "and suffering as a dart, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn36.5:2.3"
msgid "Adukkhamasukhaṃ santaṃ, "
msgstr "and that peaceful, neutral feeling "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn36.5:2.4"
msgid "addakkhi naṃ aniccato. "
msgstr "as impermanent "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn36.5:3.1"
msgid "Sa ve sammaddaso bhikkhu, "
msgstr "sees rightly; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn36.5:3.2"
msgid "parijānāti vedanā; "
msgstr "they completely understand feelings. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn36.5:3.3"
msgid "So vedanā pariññāya, "
msgstr "Completely understanding feelings, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn36.5:3.4"
msgid "diṭṭhe dhamme anāsavo; "
msgstr "they’re without defilements in this very life. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn36.5:3.5"
msgid "Kāyassa bhedā dhammaṭṭho, "
msgstr "That knowledge-master is grounded in the teaching; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn36.5:3.6"
msgid "saṅkhyaṃ nopeti vedagū”ti. "
msgstr "when their body breaks up, they can’t be reckoned.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn36.5:3.7"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
